translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どんな時も前を向くレリコフ、ポジティブ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lerikoff who always looks ahead, positive

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 強いなこの子と憧れを持ってしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She's so strong; I can't help but admire her.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうしているうちにガヤガヤ音がして
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While we were like that, a noisy sound was heard.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 仲間達が救出に現れた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our comrades appeared to rescue us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス、リセット、乱義、長田君。そしてヒーローもいる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Zansu, Reset, Rangii, Nagata-kun. And Hero was there too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レリコフはヒーローに抱きつく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lerikoff hugs Hero.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 巨大戦艦遺跡に到着する、中に入るとテラが出迎えてくれた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We arrived at the massive battleship ruins; inside, Terra welcomed us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 預かっていた　木のオーブ　を渡してくれる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She handed over the wooden orb she had been keeping.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 帰ろうとした時、地震のように揺れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As we were about to leave, it shook like an earthquake.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 我らの宿敵ジャハルッカスが蘇って暴れている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our arch-enemy Jaharukkasu has revived and is rampaging.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 我々ではとうてい敵わなかったので
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We were absolutely no match for him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今、アームズという冒険者に退治をお願いしている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Right now, we're asking an adventurer named Arms to defeat him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんでも世界最強のハンターだそうだ、任せていたら大丈夫だろう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Apparently, he's the world's strongest hunter; it should be fine leaving it to him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その戦いの振動と思われる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems to be the tremors from that battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アームズさんが？　ボク達もいきますとそこへ案内してもらう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arms-san? We will go too, so they guided us there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 通路を進む・・途中で振動が何度か聞こえる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We proceeded down the passage... several vibrations were felt along the way.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 案内のホルスがジャハルッカスの説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Horus, our guide, explained about Jaharukkasu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスさん、そうでね、貴方方のお父さんが前に倒しました
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance-san, yes, your father defeated him before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、復活してしまった、理由は分からないがこの星の悪魔と契約を結んだらしい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But he revived; the reason is unknown, but it seems he made a contract with a demon of this planet.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コールドスリープ室
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The cryo-sleep chamber.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 巨大なジャハルッカスとアームズが戦っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The gigantic Jaharukkasu and Arms are fighting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: が、明らかにアームズが押されている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But clearly, Arms is being pushed back.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アームズが倒れた（悪性けほけほ病のせいでなく実力で負けた）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arms fell (not because of the malignant cough disease, but defeated by power).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 入れ替わるようにエール達がジャハルッカスの前に立ち塞がる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eiru and the others stepped up to block Jaharukkasu as if replacing him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 君達は・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You guys are...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お久しぶりです、ここは任せて下さい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Long time no see, leave this to us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Battle

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール達がジャハルッカスを倒す。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eiru and the others defeated Jaharukkasu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを見てアームズ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seeing that, Arms said,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 強い、この子達は強くなった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Strong. These kids have gotten stronger."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この化け物＝ジャハルッカスは魔人クラスの強さがあった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This monster, Jaharukkasu, had the strength of a demon-class being.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今日は私は病気の影響も少なく万全だった、装備も世界最強クラスを揃えた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Today, I was in full health with little effect from my illness, equipped with the world's strongest gear.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それで勝てなかったのに・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And yet, I couldn't win...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ミックスがアームズの　悪性けほけほ病を直す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mix healed Arms' malignant cough disease.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールが再度、冒険に力を貸して欲しいというと今度は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When Eiru asked again to lend strength to the adventure, this time,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール達の実力を認め、参加してくれる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He acknowledged Eiru and the others' strength and agreed to join.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 助けてくれた事をお礼したい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I want to thank you for helping us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今から、日光を治しにシーウィードに行く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From now, we will go to Seaweed to cure Nikkou.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 再び、シーウィードに到着
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arrived again at Seaweed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 酒場
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tavern

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 超高級の宿でもある、アームズにはみんなにご馳走した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Also an ultra-luxury inn; Arms treated everyone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 日光を直す方法についての話し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We talked about the method to cure Nikkou.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールはあれからこんなに仲間が増えた事を語る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eiru talks about how much his group has grown since then.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス．兄妹でない者を仲間に入れるのは反対だが、アームズさんは特別だな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Zansu: I oppose letting non-siblings join the group, but Arms-san is special.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: と実績をほめつつ、色香にちょっと惑わされている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While praising his achievements, he's slightly bewitched by her beauty.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私は日光を連れて部屋にいっている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I took Nikkou along and went to the room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうそう、君達も、もし興味があればここを経験したらいい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: By the way, if you guys are interested, you should try this place.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全員分の料金はもう払っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The fee for everyone has already been paid.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まじっすかー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Really?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンスに連れられて売春に行く・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Led by Zansu, we went to the brothel...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 元就、使い慣れしている（おっさん）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Motonari is experienced in this (old man).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 長田君、ハニーでもいいですかー　おさわりー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata-kun: Hanny, is it okay? Touch touch~

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あまり激しいのは死んでしまうので　　命がけかな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If it's too rough, I might die, so it's a matter of life and death.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ドッス、ワッスは普通に居る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Doss and Wass are normally present.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 乱義はいない、こういうのには参加しない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rangii isn't here; he doesn't participate in these things.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どんな時も前を向くレリコフ、ポジティブ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lerikoff who always looks ahead, positive

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 強いなこの子と憧れを持ってしまう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She's so strong; I can't help but admire her.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうしているうちにガヤガヤ音がして
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While we were like that, a noisy sound was heard.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 仲間達が救出に現れた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our comrades appeared to rescue us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス、リセット、乱義、長田君。そしてヒーローもいる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Zansu, Reset, Rangii, Nagata-kun. And Hero was there too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レリコフはヒーローに抱きつく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lerikoff hugs Hero.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 巨大戦艦遺跡に到着する、中に入るとテラが出迎えてくれた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We arrived at the massive battleship ruins; inside, Terra welcomed us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 預かっていた　木のオーブ　を渡してくれる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She handed over the wooden orb she had been keeping.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 帰ろうとした時、地震のように揺れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As we were about to leave, it shook like an earthquake.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 我らの宿敵ジャハルッカスが蘇って暴れている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our arch-enemy Jaharukkasu has revived and is rampaging.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 我々ではとうてい敵わなかったので
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We were absolutely no match for him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今、アームズという冒険者に退治をお願いしている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Right now, we're asking an adventurer named Arms to defeat him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんでも世界最強のハンターだそうだ、任せていたら大丈夫だろう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Apparently, he's the world's strongest hunter; it should be fine leaving it to him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その戦いの振動と思われる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems to be the tremors from that battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アームズさんが？　ボク達もいきますとそこへ案内してもらう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arms-san? We will go too, so they guided us there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 通路を進む・・途中で振動が何度か聞こえる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We proceeded down the passage... several vibrations were felt along the way.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 案内のホルスがジャハルッカスの説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Horus, our guide, explained about Jaharukkasu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスさん、そうでね、貴方方のお父さんが前に倒しました
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance-san, yes, your father defeated him before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、復活してしまった、理由は分からないがこの星の悪魔と契約を結んだらしい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But he revived; the reason is unknown, but it seems he made a contract with a demon of this planet.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コールドスリープ室
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The cryo-sleep chamber.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 巨大なジャハルッカスとアームズが戦っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The gigantic Jaharukkasu and Arms are fighting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: が、明らかにアームズが押されている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But clearly, Arms is being pushed back.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アームズが倒れた（悪性けほけほ病のせいでなく実力で負けた）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arms fell (not because of the malignant cough disease, but defeated by power).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 入れ替わるようにエール達がジャハルッカスの前に立ち塞がる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eiru and the others stepped up to block Jaharukkasu as if replacing him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 君達は・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You guys are...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お久しぶりです、ここは任せて下さい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Long time no see, leave this to us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Battle

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール達がジャハルッカスを倒す。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eiru and the others defeated Jaharukkasu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを見てアームズ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seeing that, Arms said,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 強い、この子達は強くなった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Strong. These kids have gotten stronger."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この化け物＝ジャハルッカスは魔人クラスの強さがあった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This monster, Jaharukkasu, had the strength of a demon-class being.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今日は私は病気の影響も少なく万全だった、装備も世界最強クラスを揃えた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Today, I was in full health with little effect from my illness, equipped with the world's strongest gear.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それで勝てなかったのに・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And yet, I couldn't win...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ミックスがアームズの　悪性けほけほ病を直す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mix healed Arms' malignant cough disease.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールが再度、冒険に力を貸して欲しいというと今度は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When Eiru asked again to lend strength to the adventure, this time,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エール達の実力を認め、参加してくれる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He acknowledged Eiru and the others' strength and agreed to join.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 助けてくれた事をお礼したい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I want to thank you for helping us.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今から、日光を治しにシーウィードに行く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From now, we will go to Seaweed to cure Nikkou.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 再び、シーウィードに到着
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arrived again at Seaweed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 酒場
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tavern

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 超高級の宿でもある、アームズにはみんなにご馳走した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Also an ultra-luxury inn; Arms treated everyone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 日光を直す方法についての話し
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We talked about the method to cure Nikkou.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エールはあれからこんなに仲間が増えた事を語る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eiru talks about how much his group has grown since then.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス．兄妹でない者を仲間に入れるのは反対だが、アームズさんは特別だな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Zansu: I oppose letting non-siblings join the group, but Arms-san is special.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: と実績をほめつつ、色香にちょっと惑わされている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While praising his achievements, he's slightly bewitched by her beauty.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私は日光を連れて部屋にいっている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I took Nikkou along and went to the room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうそう、君達も、もし興味があればここを経験したらいい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: By the way, if you guys are interested, you should try this place.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全員分の料金はもう払っている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The fee for everyone has already been paid.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まじっすかー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Really?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンスに連れられて売春に行く・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Led by Zansu, we went to the brothel...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 元就、使い慣れしている（おっさん）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Motonari is experienced in this (old man).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 長田君、ハニーでもいいですかー　おさわりー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata-kun: Hanny, is it okay? Touch touch~

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あまり激しいのは死んでしまうので　　命がけかな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If it's too rough, I might die, so it's a matter of life and death.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ドッス、ワッスは普通に居る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Doss and Wass are normally present.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 乱義はいない、こういうのには参加しない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rangii isn't here; he doesn't participate in these things.
